{"tid":1682424,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[要人] IVE 赤腳遊行 4/11 要fa","createTime":"2019-10-30T04:50:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-30T10:35:09.000Z","uid":187232,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"53c3cd4b95e817afd3c3a47c7528cfa5b6d30ac5","tid":1682424,"uid":187232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T04:50:55.000Z","msg":"我係發起人, 以下講嘢會有啲長氣, 希望各位手足睇落去支持<br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/f23QD6oKwnI?t=13115\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Ff23QD6oKwnI%3Ft%3D13115&d=EOIuueFNblo0QISdjyyt36hYowssEfWxGXKUUX6%2FcpY%3D&h=ac73f890\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/f23QD6oKwnI?t=13115</a><br />\n\t<br />\n集合地點: 調景嶺HKDI <br />\n日期: 11月4日, 下星期一<br />\n時間: 晚上7:30<br />\n<br />\n首先, 多謝<span style=\"color: orange;\"> youtuber 燒車</span>拍條親身實驗追尋真相嘅片<br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/-KYCJ_y0SM8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F-KYCJ_y0SM8&d=EOIuueFNblo0QISdjyyt36hYowssEfWxGXKUUX6%2FcpY%3D&h=d46bdd24\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/-KYCJ_y0SM8</a><br />\n\t<br />\n由上星期睇完條片比 燒車 感動, 啟發我決心發起IVE赤腳遊行 由IVE 行去海濱, 身體力行一次呢條所為嘅彥霖赤腳自殺之路<br />\n都掙扎咗好耐<br />\n因為好多人都覺得 赤腳行石屎路好痴線<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">對腳會爆血架啵!</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">如果比藍絲打咪走唔到?!?!</span><br />\n直到噚日見到HKDI同學們仲係一直冇放棄為彥霖追尋真相, 我決定一定要搞起 赤腳行<br />\n好想為HKDI同學提供多一個方式去為追尋真相做突破<br />\n其實早幾日喺新城市撞到 燒車，佢話真係搞嘅話通知聲佢, 佢都會出席<br />\n<br />\n呢個HKDI赤腳遊行,唔係想證明啲咩比藍絲知, 唔係<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">而係想我地兄弟手足身體力行去感受，如果自己都行呢條自殺石屎路到行到痛到飛起 爆哂血，咁班黑警指彥霖赤腳行去海濱係幾咁荒謬</span><br />\n利申我唔信彥霖係自殺<br />\n利申我唔信彥霖係自殺<br />\n利申我唔信彥霖係自殺<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">但就算有1%可能, 係彥霖真係如佢個赤腳行過去，我亦想大家去感受下, 比林鄭同黑警迫死嘅彥霖, 呢條自殺路到底係有幾痛苦.....</span><br />\n<br />\n真相, 大家都好努力搵, 但可能...<br />\n我地呢一世都搵唔到<br />\n亦可能, 真相...<br />\n係大家都接受唔到咁痛心<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">HKDI赤腳遊行, 旨在要大家用真實行動, 赤腳行去海濱, 以血以痛去銘記逝去嘅彥霖<br />\n我地香港人一定會為妳繼續行落去抗爭<br />\n再痛再血, 都繼續追擊迫死妳嘅人渣, 為妳討回公道!!!</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LX8NGYq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLX8NGYq.jpg&h=390d3ef1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c5fd245acbd155902f3a27e0b9dfd21e48cf17dd","tid":1682424,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T04:51:02.000Z","msg":"我們早前在Telegram成立了手足匿名搵工平台，助手足自行尋找明白其情況的本地良心僱主，幫助他們在漫長保釋（可能講緊一、兩年時間的排期）或長期夢境中，有工開有野做有糧出，同時又可以滿足保釋條件。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1680524\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1680524</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/findagoodboss\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ffindagoodboss&d=EOIuueFNblo0QISdjyyt36hYowssEfWxGXKUUX6%2FcpY%3D&h=b400fd09\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/findagoodboss</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31252863b5ed743453d693b8a10eff202a0236dc","tid":1682424,"uid":144849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T04:55:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3cfbf17bb73ab85fc92fd6dd2b9323767fcd9f9a","tid":1682424,"uid":187232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T04:57:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"39f9ae674e23ac5bb21bcadf54ddf83ab98162d6","tid":1682424,"uid":220685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T10:35:09.000Z","msg":"推 支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw<br />\nRespect燒車🙇🏻&zwj;♂️🙇🏻&zwj;♂️"}]}